@startuml
!theme plain
title SD-05: 포획 결과 및 수족관 도감

actor Player
participant "FishController\n<<IFish>>" as FC
participant "AccountManager\n<<IAccountService>>" as AM
participant "FeedbackManager\n<<IFeedbackService>>" as FM
participant "FishingRodController\n<<IFishingRod>>" as FRC
participant "GameFlowManager\n<<IGameFlowManager>>" as GFM
participant "GameSettingsSO" as GS

== 포획 연출 ==
FC -> FC : MoveToPlayerView()
FM -> FM : PlaySound("Fanfare")
FM -> FM : ShowVisualEffect("Fireworks", fishPos)

== 물고기 상호작용 ==
loop 플레이어 터치
  Player -> FC : Touch/Rotate [보조 컨트롤러]
  FM -> FM : PlayHaptic(LightPulse, Sub)
  FM -> FM : PlaySound("FishFlop")
end

== 정보 표시 ==
FM -> FM : ShowUI("FishInfoPanel", fishData)
note right
  어종, 크기, 무게, 등급 등
  크고 대비가 뚜렷한 글씨체
end note
FM -> FM : PlayTTS("붕어를 잡으셨습니다!\n무게는 2.3kg입니다")

== 확인 처리 ==
alt 수동: 버튼 클릭
  Player -> FM : Press("ConfirmButton")
  FM -> FM : PlaySound("ButtonClick")
  FM -> FM : PlayHaptic(LightPulse, Sub)
else 자동: autoConfirmDelay 경과
  GS -> GS : autoConfirmDelay (10초)
  ...10초 경과 시 자동 확인...
end

== 도감 저장 ==
AM -> AM : AddToEncyclopedia(fishCatchData)
AM -> AM : SaveAccount()
FM -> FM : ShowVisualEffect("FishToAquarium")
FM -> FM : HideUI("FishInfoPanel")

== 상태 복귀 ==
FRC -> FRC : state = Idle
GFM -> GFM : TransitionTo(FishingReady)

@enduml